AMEND S e n ate Bill No. 2443* House Bill No. 2474
by deleting all language after the enacting clause and substituting:
SECTION 1. Tennessee Code Annotated, Section 55-8-198(l)(1)(A), is amended by
adding "when a warning flasher or flashers are in operation or during times when children are
present" immediately following "Within the designated distance of a marked school zone".
SECTION 2. This act takes effect July 1, 2026, the public welfare requiring it.
